title: 34: Mini Bachelorette Reunion Recap
itunes:title: 34: Mini Bachelorette Reunion Recap
description:
The Broads do a quick recap of ABC’s “historical” Bachelorette Reunion in preparation of The Beast’s season. They talk buses, Botox, breaking beds, Bundy, and a little bit of Hannah B! They also announce the official start of an added Thursday episode!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
